# CI/CD Specific Focus
- All workflows must be idempotent and support dry-run where possible.
- Changes to deployment must consider impact on Backend, NodeAgent, and App repositories.
- Always reference TASK-XXXX in commit messages and PRs.
- Prefer GitHub Actions + reusable workflows from central docs when possible.